"       Camptosar (irinotecan hydrochloride) injection. US FDA approved manufacturer's package insert. US National Library of Medicine. (Available online at dailymed.nlm.nih.gov, accessed on December 16, 2011).",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Fluorouracil injection. US FDA approved manufacturer's package insert. US National Library of Medicine. (Available online at dailymed.nlm.nih.gov, accessed on December 28, 2011.",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Conroy T, et al. N Engl J Med 2011; 364:1817.",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Fusilev (levoleucovorin calcium) injection. US FDA-approved manufacturer's package insert. US National Library of Medicine. (Available online at dailymed.nlm.nih.gov, accessed on December 16, 2011).",
"      </li>",
"     </ol>",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
